Members of 2006/2007 set of the Faculty of Law, Olabisi Onabanjo University (OOU), Ago-Iwoye, Ogun State will hold a re-union in Lagos this Sunday. Spokesman of the Reconvene Organizing Committee, David Ashaolu McAsh said the event, tagged: #Reconvene2019, is scheduled for the Radisson Hotel, GRA, Ikeja on December 22, 2019. Ashaolu McAsh said: “12 years is a good time to meet again and reminisce on their gains and achievements and how they have impacted the lives of other members of the society.” He said the event will also feature the launch of a Reunion Magazine and a Career Intervention Programme for their alma mata.